        ": \" إذا أقيمت الصلاة حرم الكلام على الامام وأهل المسجد إلا في تقديم إمام."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1137 – Zurarah narrated from Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as) that He said:\n\"When the prayer has been established (by the iqamah), speaking becomes forbidden for the Imam and the people of the mosque, except in the matter of appointing an Imam”."
        ]
